7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Bardeen and Relay.app share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. On the other hand, Relay.app uniquely offers Error Handling and Team Collaboration and Webhook Support, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Bardeen holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Relay.app scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Bardeen and Relay.app offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Bardeen's free tier and Relay.app's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
